OpenCPN DB Probe Commands (Pi venv path)

Use these on the Raspberry Pi:

/home/pi/pi-deck-tools/.venv/bin/python /home/pi/pi-deck-tools/apps/opencpn_db_probe.py --tables
/home/pi/pi-deck-tools/.venv/bin/python /home/pi/pi-deck-tools/apps/opencpn_db_probe.py --routes
/home/pi/pi-deck-tools/.venv/bin/python /home/pi/pi-deck-tools/apps/opencpn_db_probe.py --columns waypoint
/home/pi/pi-deck-tools/.venv/bin/python /home/pi/pi-deck-tools/apps/opencpn_db_probe.py --route "My Route Name"
/home/pi/pi-deck-tools/.venv/bin/python /home/pi/pi-deck-tools/apps/opencpn_db_probe.py --route "My Route Name" --json
